snippet.title: a Friend or Foe
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel! I use this as a creative outlet, I AM NOT PAID so I basically upload whatever I want whenever I want. I am a medical coder and a chemist. I do not claim to be anything other than that professionally. 

I love hearing from people and their opinions. But just know that if you are attacking people and spam hating that is against guidelines and I will have to take it down. There's enough pain in the world let's not add unnecessary suffering to it. Be mindful of those around you. 

Feel free to give me recommendations! Or message me if you have any questions. I swear I don't bite.
